The paper deals with the joint training of images and captions, and the generation of new captions given either an image or a caption query. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of deep neural networks and the evaluation on multiple tasks suggests that the paper may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with cross-modal retrieval, which involves searching for relevant information across different modalities, suggesting that it may also belong to the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
